    • Uses of IField in org.modelio.api.ui.form.fields

      Classes in org.modelio.api.ui.form.fields that implement IField 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AbstractField
      An abstract implementation of IField composed of: a Label an edition control a help button a help text
      The composite field controls are layouted as follows:
      [--- label ---] [-------- edition control -------- ] [---button --- ]
      [----------- help text ------------]
      where the help text if folded/unfolded by the help button.
